caption:
Dear Jack and jack,
I think I deserve to with this contest because I love you guys so much. Everyday I smile when I think about you guys. Just thinking about how you love your fans and how inspiring you are to me and others. Your music cheers me up when I'm feeling down. you guys mean the world to me. you guys are in a big spot in my heart. I really would love this experience and I would love to meet both of them really soon ? #contest #contest @JackandJackOfficial @JackGilinskyOfficial @JackJohnsonOfficial
